<%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>


<header class="about-header">
    <h1>Travel Tips and Resources</h1>
</header>

<main class="about-main">
    <section id="packing-guide">
        <h2>Packing Guide</h2>
        <p>Whether you're traveling solo, with your family, or seeking adventure, packing efficiently is essential. Here are some tips:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Solo Travelers:</strong> Pack light and versatile clothing. Consider a travel-sized toiletry kit.</li>
            <li><strong>Families:</strong> Pack snacks and entertainment for kids. Bring essential medications and first-aid supplies.</li>
            <li><strong>Adventure Seekers:</strong> Pack durable and waterproof gear. Don't forget a portable charger and a multi-tool.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="visa-requirements">
        <h2>Visa Requirements</h2>
        <p>Before traveling abroad, it's crucial to understand the visa requirements for your destination. Here are some general tips:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Research visa requirements well in advance of your trip.</li>
            <li>Apply for visas early to avoid delays.</li>
            <li>Check for any additional entry requirements, such as vaccinations.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="safety-tips">
        <h2>Safety Tips</h2>
        <p>Traveling safely is a top priority for all travelers. Here are some safety tips to keep in mind:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Keep your valuables secure and avoid displaying expensive items in public.</li>
            <li>Stay aware of your surroundings and trust your instincts.</li>
            <li>Research local emergency numbers and healthcare facilities.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="cultural-etiquettes">
        <h2>Cultural Etiquettes</h2>
        <p>Respecting local customs and cultural etiquettes is essential while traveling. Here are some tips:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Research cultural norms and customs before visiting a new destination.</li>
            <li>Learn basic greetings and phrases in the local language.</li>
            <li>Observe and follow local customs regarding dress code and behavior.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="checklist">
        <h2>Interactive Checklist</h2>
        <p>Use this interactive checklist to plan your trip and ensure you don't forget any essential items:</p>
        <form id="packing-checklist">
            <label for="clothing"><input type="checkbox" id="clothing" name="clothing"> Clothing</label><br>
            <label for="toiletries"><input type="checkbox" id="toiletries" name="toiletries"> Toiletries</label><br>
            <label for="medications"><input type="checkbox" id="medications" name="medications"> Medications</label><br>
            <label for="passport"><input type="checkbox" id="passport" name="passport"> Passport</label><br>
            <label for="tickets"><input type="checkbox" id="tickets" name="tickets"> Tickets</label><br>
            <label for="money"><input type="checkbox" id="money" name="money"> Money/Currency</label><br>
            <label for="documents"><input type="checkbox" id="documents" name="documents"> Travel Documents</label><br>
            <label for="charger"><input type="checkbox" id="charger" name="charger"> Phone Charger</label><br>
            <label for="adapter"><input type="checkbox" id="adapter" name="adapter"> Power Adapter</label><br>
            <label for="camera"><input type="checkbox" id="camera" name="camera"> Camera</label><br>
            <label for="snacks"><input type="checkbox" id="snacks" name="snacks"> Snacks</label><br>
            <label for="first-aid"><input type="checkbox" id="first-aid" name="first-aid"> First Aid Kit</label><br>

        </form>
    </section>
</main>
